I don't understand why people say it's P2W. You can unlock every tower and upgrade in less then 10 hours of playing.
In-game there is no way to be in any advantage. This game is not p2w in any way. Just had to be said.

Personal opinion on this game:
-10/10 game no arguing with that.;
-always fun, even after 4 streight hours of playing;
-very addictive;
-A lot of towers to choose from;
-Amazing club room integration once every 2 hours or one time 5$ for unlimited club rooms.
